    {
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "chapterTitle": "八",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_14_1865-1995",
          "range": "1865-1995",
          "rangeStart": 1865,
          "rangeEnd": 1995,
          "markText": "天下只有两种人。譬如一串葡萄到手，一种人挑最好的先吃，另一种人把最好的留在最后吃。照例第一种人应该乐观，因为他每吃一颗都是吃剩的葡萄里最好的；第二种人应该悲观，因为他每吃一颗都是吃剩的葡萄里最坏的。不过事实上适得其反，缘故是第二种人还有希望，第一种人只有回忆。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749460855,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-09 17:20:55",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1865&rangeEnd=1995",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1865&rangeEnd=1995"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "chapterTitle": "七",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_13_18609-18635",
          "range": "18609-18635",
          "rangeStart": 18609,
          "rangeEnd": 18635,
          "markText": "女人出门，照例忘掉东西，所以一次出门事实上等于两次。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749443800,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-09 12:36:40",
          "chapterUid": 13,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=18609&rangeEnd=18635",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=18609&rangeEnd=18635"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "三",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_9_48487-48542",
          "range": "48489-48544",
          "rangeStart": 48489,
          "rangeEnd": 48544,
          "markText": "这一分钟好长，她等不及了，正要分付女用人，鸿渐忽然回过脸来，狗抖毛似的抖擞身子，像把周围的雨抖出去，开步走了。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749292310,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:31:50",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=48489&rangeEnd=48544",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=48489&rangeEnd=48544"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_9_48290-48349",
          "range": "48292-48351",
          "rangeStart": 48292,
          "rangeEnd": 48351,
          "markText": "有时候，“不再坐一会么？”可以撵走人，有时候“再会”可以挽留人；唐小姐挽不住方鸿渐，所以加一句“希望你远行一路平安”。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749292265,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:31:05",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=48292&rangeEnd=48351",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=48292&rangeEnd=48351"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_9_47965-48038",
          "range": "47967-48040",
          "rangeStart": 47967,
          "rangeEnd": 48040,
          "markText": "鸿渐身心仿佛通电似的发麻，只知道唐小姐在说自己，没心思来领会她话里的意义，好比头脑里蒙上一层油纸，她的话雨点似的渗不进，可是油纸震颤着雨打的重量。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749292176,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:29:36",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=47967&rangeEnd=48040",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=47967&rangeEnd=48040"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300027701_9_37844-37889",
          "range": "37845-37890",
          "rangeStart": 37845,
          "rangeEnd": 37890,
          "markText": "结婚仿佛金漆的鸟笼，笼子外面的鸟想住进去，笼内的鸟想飞出来；所以结而离，离而结，没有了局。",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749186024,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-06 13:00:24",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37845&rangeEnd=37890",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=37845&rangeEnd=37890"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
