    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300027701_7_5342-5363",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5342-5363",
      "markText": "汝托词悲秋，吾知汝实为怀春，难逃老夫洞鉴也",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5342&rangeEnd=5363",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5342&rangeEnd=5363"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300027701_7_419-501",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "419-501",
      "markText": "但是太阳依然不饶人地迟落早起，侵占去大部分的夜。夜仿佛纸浸了油，变成半透明体；它给太阳拥抱住了，分不出身来，也许是给太阳陶醉了，所以夕照晚霞隐褪后的夜色也带着酡红。",
      "totalCount": 308,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300027701&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=419&rangeEnd=501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/67632fe0813ab7152g011ed4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=419&rangeEnd=501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300027701_11_16546-16604",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "16546-16604",
      "markText": "每逢它不肯走，汽车夫就破口臭骂，此刻骂得更利害了。骂来骂去，只有一个意思：汽车夫愿意跟汽车的母亲和祖母发生肉体恋爱。",
